+    Formula from "Explanatory Supplement to the Astronomical Almanac" 2006, derived from Fliegel & Van Flandern 1968
+    jd = ( 3 + ( 11 * year ) ) / 30 + 354 * year + 30 * month - ( month - 1 ) / 2 + day + epoch().toJulianDay() - 385;
+    */
+}
